{"article_id":"JX22zts5r1ZvjDUE","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON ( ) -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"U.S. President Donald Trump on Monday said","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"he was ordering the creation of a sixth branch of the military","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"to focus on space ,","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"a move","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"critics said","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"could harm the Air Force .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"\" It is not enough to merely have an American presence in space .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"We must have American dominance in space , \"","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"Trump said before a meeting of his National Space Council .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"\" We are going to have the Air Force","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"and we ' re going to have the ' Space Force. '","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"Separate but equal .","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"It is going to be something , \"","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"he said later .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"The United States is a member of the 1967 Outer Space Treaty ,","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"which bars the stationing of weapons of mass destruction in space","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"and only allows for the use of the moon and other celestial bodies for peaceful purposes .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"The idea of a Space Force has been raised before , by Trump and previous administrations ,","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"with proponents saying","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"it would make the Pentagon more efficient .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"It has also faced criticism from senior military officials .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"Air Force Chief of Staff General David Goldfein told a 2017 congressional hearing","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"that creating a new space branch would \" move us in the wrong direction. \"","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"The Air Force oversees most of the country ' s space-related military activity .","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"The move would require the budgetary approval of the U.S. Congress ,","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"which has been divided on the idea .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"\" Thankfully , the president can ' t do it","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"without Congress","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"because now is NOT the time","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"to rip the Air Force apart .","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"Too many missions at stake , \"","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"U.S . Senator Bill Nelson , a Democrat , said on Twitter .","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"Pentagon spokeswoman Dana White said","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"the department ' s policy board would prepare to implement Trump ' s order .","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"\" Working with Congress ,","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"this will be a deliberate process with a great deal of input from multiple stakeholders , \"","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"White said in a statement .","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"In December , the president signed a directive","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"that","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"he said","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"would enable astronauts to return to the moon","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"and eventually lead a mission to Mars .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"He has ordered the government to review regulations on commercial space flights .","depth":4},{"id":44,"text":"Americans first landed on the moon in 1969 ,","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"reaching a goal","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"set by former President John F. Kennedy in 1961","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"and capping a decade-long space race between Washington and Moscow .","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"Since then , U.S. efforts","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"to explore beyond the Earth ' s orbit","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"have largely focused on remote spacecraft","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"that do not have human crew members ,","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"though American presidents have raised the idea","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"of sending humans back to the moon or further .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":107,"left":0,"right":106,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":106,"left":90,"right":105,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":90,"left":70,"right":89,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":67,"right":69,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":67,"left":59,"right":66,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":59,"left":1,"right":58,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":58,"left":55,"right":57,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":55,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":57,"left":56,"right":6,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":56,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":66,"left":61,"right":65,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":61,"left":60,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":60,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":65,"left":64,"right":14,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":64,"left":63,"right":13,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":63,"left":10,"right":62,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":62,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":69,"left":15,"right":68,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":68,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":89,"left":84,"right":88,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":84,"left":76,"right":83,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":76,"left":75,"right":24,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":72,"right":74,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":72,"left":18,"right":71,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":19,"right":20,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":74,"left":21,"right":73,"relation":"ela